<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #0b0e14; color: #ffffff; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .wrapper { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%); padding: 40px; border-top: 5px solid #d4af37; }
        .logo { text-align: center; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 3px; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .logo span { color: #d4af37; }
        .icon { font-size: 40px; display: block; margin: 10px 0; color: #d4af37; text-align: center; }
        .header { text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #d4af37; padding-bottom: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        h1 { color: #d4af37; font-size: 22px; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0; }
        .content { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #e2e8f0; text-align: center; }
        .message-box { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid #d4af37; margin: 25px 0; font-style: italic; text-align: left; }
        .button { display: block; width: 220px; margin: 30px auto; padding: 15px; background: #d4af37; color: #000; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 5px; transition: 0.3s; }
        .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="logo">REBEL <span>REFINE</span></div>
        
        <div class="header">
            <span class="icon">✉️</span>
            <h1>Nouveau message reçu</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Bonjour <strong>{{ receiver.nickname }}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Vous avez reçu un nouveau message traduit de la part de <strong>{{ sender.nickname }}</strong> :</p>
            
            <div class="message-box">
                "{{ messageContent }}"
            </div>
            
            <p>Prêt à poursuivre la conversation ? Cliquez ci-dessous pour répondre.</p>
        </div>

        <a href="{{ frontendUrl }}/login" class="button">LIRE & RÉPONDRE ✉️</a>
        
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2026 Rebel Refine. Restez connecté.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>